data.description: **Seller offering $10k towards rate buy down!** Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, where natural light fills the open-concept interior. Enjoy two living areas, upgraded flooring, and the privacy of an ensuite bathroom in the primary bedroom. Outside, a fenced yard offers your own private retreat in a peaceful neighborhood. Conveniently situated with easy highway access and is only minutes from Old Town Fort Collins. This home also benefits from an HOA that covers trash removal and outdoor irrigation water (including sprinkler start up and blow outs) ensuring a hassle-free lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your new home! Schedule a tour today.
